tn btn--ghost\" data-v-f3872c14=\"\">View all showcases →</a></div></div></section><section class=\"section section--dark\" data-v-85356ec7=\"\"><div class=\"container\" data-v-85356ec7=\"\"><div class=\"text-center\" data-v-85356ec7=\"\"><h2 data-v-85356ec7=\"\">Why Teamo</h2></div><div class=\"grid grid--3 value-grid\" data-v-85356ec7=\"\"><!--[--><div class=\"card value-card\" data-v-85356ec7=\"\"><h3 data-v-85356ec7=\"\">8 models, zero API keys</h3><p class=\"text-secondary\" data-v-85356ec7=\"\">Pre-installed with the latest models including Gemini, Claude, and GPT. Pay with one unified Credits balance.</p></div><div class=\"card value-card\" data-v-85356ec7=\"\"><h3 data-v-85356ec7=\"\">Deep Research reads 1,000 papers</h3><p class=\"text-secondary\" data-v-85356ec7=\"\">SOTA-level research agent with access to trillion-scale industry databases for investment-grade reporting.</p></div><div class=\"card value-card\" data-v-85356ec7=\"\"><h3 data-v-85356ec7=\"\">Watch every step, know every credit</h3><p class=\"text-secondary\" data-v-85356ec7=\"\">Visual task trees let you observe the agent's thought process, actions, and exact credit consumption in real-time.</p></div><!--]--></div></div></section><section class=\"section\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\"><div class=\"container\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\"><div class=\"text-center\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\"><h2 data-v-0f7642f6=\"\">Get started in 3 steps</h2></div><div class=\"steps\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\"><!--[--><div class=\"step\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\"><div class=\"step__num\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\">01</div><h3 class=\"step__title\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\">Choose your setup</h3><p class=\"step__desc text-secondary\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\">Select the AI agent skills and the underlying model for your workflow.</p></div><div class=\"step\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\"><div class=\"step__num\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\">02</div><h3 class=\"step__title\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\">Give Teamo a task</h3><p class=\"step__desc text-secondary\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\">Describe your goal, from simple coding tasks to complex industry research reports.</p></div><div class=\"step\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\"><div class=\"step__num\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\">03</div><h3 class=\"step__title\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\">Wake up to results</h3><p class=\"step__desc text-secondary\" data-v-0f7642f6=\"\">Teamo works autonomously 24/7. Go to sleep and wake up to finished results.</p></div><!--]--></div></div></section><section class=\"section section--dark\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\"><div class=\"container\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\"><div class=\"text-center\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\"><h2 data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Simple, transparent pricing</h2><p class=\"section-subtitle\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\">No API keys to manage. One Credits balance for everything.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid--3 pricing-grid\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\"><!--[--><div class=\"card pricing-card\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\"><!----><h3 class=\"pricing-card__name\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Starter</h3><div class=\"pricing-card__price\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\">$29</div><div class=\"pricing-card__credits text-muted\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\">1,000 Credits / month</div><ul class=\"pricing-card__features\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\"><!--[--><li data-v-04bd1214=\"\">All 8 models included</li><li data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Basic deep research</li><li data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Single user</li><li data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Community support</li><!--]--></ul><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn--primary pricing-card__cta\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Try Free</button></div><div class=\"pricing-card--popular card pricing-card\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\"><div class=\"pricing-card__badge label label--accent\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Most popular</div><h3 class=\"pricing-card__name\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Pro</h3><div class=\"pricing-card__price\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\">$99</div><div class=\"pricing-card__credits text-muted\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\">5,000 Credits / month</div><ul class=\"pricing-card__features\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\"><!--[--><li data-v-04bd1214=\"\">All 8 models included</li><li data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Advanced deep research</li><li data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Priority task queue</li><li data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Email support</li><!--]--></ul><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn--primary pricing-card__cta\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Try Free</button></div><div class=\"card pricing-card\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\"><!----><h3 class=\"pricing-card__name\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Team</h3><div class=\"pricing-card__price\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\">$299</div><div class=\"pricing-card__credits text-muted\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\">20,000 Credits / month</div><ul class=\"pricing-card__features\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\"><!--[--><li data-v-04bd1214=\"\">All 8 models included</li><li data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Unlimited deep research</li><li data-v-04bd1214=\"\">5 team seats</li><li data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Dedicated account manager</li><li data-v-04bd1214=\"\">API access</li><!--]--></ul><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn--primary pricing-card__cta\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\">Try Free</button></div><!--]--></div><div class=\"text-center pricing-footer\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\"><a href=\"/en/pricing\" class=\"btn btn--ghost\" data-v-04bd1214=\"\">See full pricing details →</a></div></div></section><section class=\"section\" data-v-e407f93a=\"\"><div class=\"container faq-container\" data-v-e407f93a=\"\"><div class=\"text-center\" data-v-e407f93a=\"\"><h2 data-v-e407f93a=\"\">Frequently asked questions</h2></div><div class=\"faq-list\" data-v-e407f93a=\"\"><!--[--><details data-v-e407f93a=\"\"><summary data-v-e407f93a=\"\">What is Teamo Machine?</summary><p data-v-e407f93a=\"\">Teamo is an autonomous AI agent platform that works 24/7. You can delegate tasks like deep research, coding, design, and market monitoring — it completes them autonomously in the cloud.</p></details><details data-v-e407f93a=\"\"><summary data-v-e407f93a=\"\">How is Teamo different from OpenClaw?</summary><p data-v-e407f93a=\"\">Unlike the self-hosted OpenClaw, Teamo is fully cloud-hosted with zero coding required. No technical background needed — just sign up and start.</p></details><details data-v-e407f93a=\"\"><summary data-v-e407f93a=\"\">Do I need to write code or configure API keys?</summary><p data-v-e407f93a=\"\">No coding and no API keys required. Teamo uses a unified Credits system that replaces complex API key management. All models share one balance.</p></details><details data-v-e407f93a=\"\"><summary data-v-e407f93a=\"\">What are Credits and are they enough?</summary><p data-v-e407f93a=\"\">Credits are the universal AI compute currency. 1 Credit covers approximately one standard AI conversation. New users get 1,000 free Credits — enough for dozens of tasks.</p></details><details data-v-e407f93a=\"\"><summary data-v-e407f93a=\"\">What AI models are supported?</summary><p data-v-e407f93a=\"\">We support 8+ top-tier models out-of-the-box, including Claude Sonnet 4.6, GPT-5.4, Gemini 1.5 Pro, DeepSeek-V3, and more. Continuously updated.</p></details><details data-v-e407f93a=\"\"><summary data-v-e407f93a=\"\">Is my data secure?</summary><p data-v-e407f93a=\"\">Absolutely. All tasks run in isolated cloud sandbox environments with full task-level isolation. We maintain SOC2 audit compliance.</p></details><!--]--></div></div></section><section class=\"section final-cta\" data-v-1ca41e6b=\"\"><div class=\"container text-center\" data-v-1ca41e6b=\"\"><h2 class=\"final-cta__title\" data-v-1ca41e6b=\"\">Your AI team is ready</h2><p class=\"final-cta__subtitle\" data-v-1ca41e6b=\"\">Sign up free and get 1,000 Credits instantly</p><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn--primary btn--large\" data-v-1ca41e6b=\"\">Create My Teamo Agent →</button></div></section></div></main><footer id=\"footer\" class=\"footer\" data-v-ab2eb0b3=\"\" data-v-8a600af6=\"\"><div class=\"container footer__inner\" data-v-8a600af6=\"\"><div class=\"footer__top\" data-v-8a600af6=\"\"><div class=\"footer__brand\" data-v-8a600af6=\"\"><a aria-current=\"page\" href=\"/en\" class=\"router-link-active